casebody.data:
No. 108,

Orig.

Nebraska v. Wyoming et al. [For earlier order herein, see, e. g., ante, p. 917.]

Sixth motion of the Special Master for compensation and reimbursement of expenses granted, and the Special Master is awarded a total of $233,144.11. Assessment of this award is deferred pending receipt of further responses by Colorado and the amici curiae to the special assessment proposed by the Special Master, to be filed on or before Monday, May 4, 1992, and further order of the Court.
